Nigerian music star, Damilola Afolabi aka L.A.X has featured DMW boss, Davido, on his new single, Pepe. The young music act released the new song on his imprint, Rasaki Music Group following a collaboration with Mayorkun a few months back. L.A.X announced via his Instagram account on Thursday, June 10, 2021. L.A.X first made his entry on the Nigerian music scene with a collaboration with Wizkid in the early days of StarBoy. The singer was with the StarBoy music imprint for several years before parting ways with Wizkid to kick off his Rasaki Music Group.